*rspec-2.4.0 (15 Jan 2011)
*rspec-1.3.1-r1 (15 Jan 2011)

  15 Jan 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rspec-1.3.1-r1.ebuild,
  +rspec-2.4.0.ebuild:
  Version bump for RSpec 2.4.0. Add revision in sot 0 that no longer install
  autospec, which is now installed by rspec-core.

  27 Dec 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -rspec-1.3.0.ebuild,
  -rspec-1.3.0-r1.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

  02 Dec 2010; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> rspec-1.3.1.ebuild,
  rspec-2.0.0_beta22.ebuild:
  Marked ~x64-macos

  25 Oct 2010; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> rspec-1.3.0-r1.ebuild,
  rspec-1.3.1.ebuild, rspec-2.0.0_beta22.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #337956).

